{"tid":501514,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個你覺得係真理嘅人性","createTime":"2017-12-17T02:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T16:01:43.000Z","uid":13251,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"be626188388261248950da18cda492d911b38a5b","tid":501514,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:36:56.000Z","msg":"唔好性本善惡咁膚淺<br />\n一齊黎講下唔同嘅人性<br />\n<br />\n首先我覺得人性係天生自私嘅<br />\n所有人都係先諗自己 再諗他人<br />\n<br />\n孔子深明人性先講推己及人<br />\n將自私合理化 普遍人會比較容易接受規範<br />\n<br />\n大家開冷氣暖氣嘅時候只會諗到自己舒服<br />\n唔會理後代 將來 污染等問題<br />\n你有認同嗎 沒有 因為你只想到自己<br />\n<br />\n大家講下仲有無其他人性係好明顯嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd08d6c0c61a1cb3ba6f1e9544eaee72f0834634","tid":501514,"uid":41355,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/104508_ec69219a78ea90b5af9da109e61214f0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F104508_ec69219a78ea90b5af9da109e61214f0.gif&h=426215fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"359b042b1f1f4ba993e2b0f13b7665e88ddc2a98","tid":501514,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:47:50.000Z","msg":"Self-improvement is masturbation<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79be487254365361ac8a4f1885be590e938f6632","tid":501514,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:59:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Self-improvement is masturbation<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打飛機都叫人性？<br />\n定你想講男人天性鹹濕？"},{"pid":"bfe1ceb46e60ccb5e4ef730c4359366cb6184648","tid":501514,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:01:45.000Z","msg":"人與人之間只得利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e5ffaac97a3594c780200505cb8697f291e371","tid":501514,"uid":86288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:16:39.000Z","msg":"冇討論空間<br />\n任何如果冇左規範 而你又有慾望/衝動想做 就係人性<br />\n記住 呢個世界冇聖人 只有偽善<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f97d13309fc2dc71cb2c9bf8117e12873816578","tid":501514,"uid":88033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:23:47.000Z","msg":"所謂為他人設想都係自私既行為，人既自由意志本身已經構成惡"},{"pid":"278111b4f961c71ec60e9371b4711fb77ccebc8d","tid":501514,"uid":154800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:25:34.000Z","msg":"呢個topic自古以來都係得一個標準答案<br />\n傾第二啲野好過啦"},{"pid":"e62b793120a859f2a392a7d88298aaf8929c6bb4","tid":501514,"uid":41355,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/113216_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F113216_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2e32fd58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b798cfb467332fbdac564f0e76e693bdb5b7f834","tid":501514,"uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T04:56:15.000Z","msg":"動物本性：要搵食和飲水＋要繁殖＋要衛生＋安全感<br />\n人類本性：動物本性＋喜歡探索世界和真理＋具抽象思維＋有文字和數字＋有金錢概念"},{"pid":"348d18a5c2f2db05036d62fcc83c27086c2afd1c","tid":501514,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:37:28.000Z","msg":"中國談性都好多唔同諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡單的說，慎到和韓非關於人性的認識可以用「因勢自為」四個字表達，亦即因應情勢，人性人情總是尋求自己最方便，自己最舒適，以及自己最有利的方式展形具現。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;許雅棠<br />\n<br />\n簡介基本古代思想概念：性 兼讀韓非子外儲說左上篇、六反篇之控制人性的趨利避害<br />\n<a href=\"http://deliver90.blogspot.tw/2017/07/ep11.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdeliver90.blogspot.tw%2F2017%2F07%2Fep11.html%3Fm%3D1&d=C9rODD4zZtdGQ3sn10KX3%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=99eb7e80\" target=\"_blank\">http://deliver90.blogspot.tw/2017/07/ep11.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"23a09ee8e11304e415ebf4a1dbf56b4e6ed35230","tid":501514,"uid":45926,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T07:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/151239_4695c702bc81210c9fbd96cf002adde3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F151239_4695c702bc81210c9fbd96cf002adde3.jpg&h=d01fc1e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3acbdfd0f173e90772069249b05ba99bf9f9bc22","tid":501514,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T15:52:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>動物本性：要搵食和飲水＋要繁殖＋要衛生＋安全感<br />\n人類本性：動物本性＋喜歡探索世界和真理＋具抽象思維＋有文字和數字＋有金錢概念</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n世界混亂和罪惡的原因：<br />\n<br />\n1 因為所有生物都要搵食<br />\n包括細菌病毒都要搵食<br />\n<br />\n2 為左防禦被獵食（恐懼與安全需求）<br />\n<br />\n3 微生物因為去宿主搵食和防禦造成的問題 (傳染病，敏感症）<br />\n<br />\n4 大腦因信息超載導致情緒失控<br />\n<br />\n5 人類獨有的抽象思維及金錢概念製造更多問題和煩惱。"},{"pid":"ac109f4e8654525e2327cb800108fc844aca7ee2","tid":501514,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T16:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>動物本性：要搵食和飲水＋要繁殖＋要衛生＋安全感<br />\n人類本性：動物本性＋喜歡探索世界和真理＋具抽象思維＋有文字和數字＋有金錢概念</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n世界混亂和罪惡的原因：<br />\n<br />\n1 因為所有生物都要搵食<br />\n包括細菌病毒都要搵食<br />\n<br />\n2 為左防禦被獵食（恐懼與安全需求）<br />\n<br />\n3 微生物因為去宿主搵食和防禦造成的問題 (傳染病，敏感症）<br />\n<br />\n4 大腦因信息超載導致情緒失控<br />\n<br />\n5 人類獨有的抽象思維及金錢概念製造更多問題和煩惱。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n6 人類社會本身就是互相合作，互相競爭。合作與競爭並存。<br />\n<br />\n7 過量繁殖導致競爭過份激烈"}]}